  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>A willing creature you touch is enhanced with a Genjutsu that makes the words they speak seem more interesting, attractive or compelling.</p><p>For the duration an affected creature has advantage on all charisma-based checks using skills to talk with another creature. When a creature who finds them even slightly attractive hears them speak, that creature must succeed a Charisma Saving throw. On a failed save that creature gains 1 rank of charmed against them for the duration.</p>",
